rComments: You really have to love the course material in order to succeed in his classes. He demands a lot of reading and his weekly reading responses are hard to do because of the difficulty of the readings. However, he is a relatively easy marker (very slow marker though so expect not to know what your mark is until the end of the course).
teacherRatingTags: ["Skip class? You won't pass.", 'Gives good feedback', 'Get ready to read']
